      "start": 593.3,
      "end": 595.3,
      "text": "어떤 상황이 안 좋아지면,"
    },
    {
      "start": 595.52,
      "end": 596.26,
      "text": "다시 말해,"
    },
    {
      "start": 596.32,
      "end": 597.38,
      "text": "문제가 생기잖아?"
    },
    {
      "start": 597.94,
      "end": 599.78,
      "text": "First thing humans do,"
    },
    {
      "start": 600.16,
      "end": 602.8,
      "text": "인간들이 하는 가장 첫 번째 일은"
    },
    {
      "start": 602.8,
      "end": 604.9,
      "text": "is get rid of the dog."
    },
    {
      "start": 605.12,
      "end": 605.52,
      "text": "라고 했어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 605.52,
      "end": 606.54,
      "text": "get rid of 하면"
    },
    {
      "start": 606.54,
      "end": 607.94,
      "text": "remove 라는 거잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 608.38,
      "end": 610.42,
      "text": "그래서 강아지를 없애는 거야?"
    },
    {
      "start": 610.78,
      "end": 611.02,
      "text": "아,"
    },
    {
      "start": 611.18,
      "end": 613.08,
      "text": "강아지부터 내다 버리는 거야."
    },
    {
      "start": 613.3,
      "end": 613.98,
      "text": "라고 이야기합니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 614.12,
      "end": 614.92,
      "text": "The dog goes."
    },
    {
      "start": 615.12,
      "end": 616.02,
      "text": "Bye-bye dog."
    },
    {
      "start": 616.1,
      "end": 616.58,
      "text": "Oh my God."
    },
    {
      "start": 616.58,
      "end": 617.8,
      "text": "The dog pooped in the house"
    },
    {
      "start": 617.8,
      "end": 619.28,
      "text": "one too many times."
    },
    {
      "start": 619.28,
      "end": 620.18,
      "text": "Bye-bye."
    },
    {
      "start": 620.18,
      "end": 620.54,
      "text": "어머,"
    },
    {
      "start": 620.98,
      "end": 621.22,
      "text": "그래요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 621.32,
      "end": 623.58,
      "text": "그것도 이유가 될 수 있군요."
    },
    {
      "start": 623.7,
      "end": 624.02,
      "text": "Sometimes."
    },
    {
      "start": 624.54,
      "end": 625.18,
      "text": "I mean,"
    },
    {
      "start": 625.22,
      "end": 626.62,
      "text": "that's a pathetic excuse though."
    },
    {
      "start": 626.66,
      "end": 628.2,
      "text": "You need to train the dog"
    },
    {
      "start": 628.2,
      "end": 629.84,
      "text": "to poop in the right place."
    },
    {
      "start": 630.06,
      "end": 630.34,
      "text": "그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 630.56,
      "end": 631.18,
      "text": "But yeah,"
    },
    {
      "start": 631.42,
      "end": 632.28,
      "text": "I guess Rousey"
    },
    {
      "start": 632.28,
      "end": 633.86,
      "text": "has a very bad experience."
    },
    {
      "start": 635.59,
      "end": 635.95,
      "text": "No,"
    },
    {
      "start": 636.39,
      "end": 637.33,
      "text": "not this girl."
    },
    {
      "start": 637.57,
      "end": 639.39,
      "text": "She's talking about herself."
    },
    {
      "start": 639.53,
      "end": 639.83,
      "text": "그렇죠."
    },
    {
      "start": 640.49,
      "end": 640.69,
      "text": "그,"
    },
    {
      "start": 640.93,
      "end": 641.63,
      "text": "조에라는"
    },
    {
      "start": 641.63,
      "end": 642.23,
      "text": "그,"
    },
    {
      "start": 642.37,
      "end": 643.17,
      "text": "girl에 대해서"
    },
    {
      "start": 643.17,
      "end": 644.73,
      "text": "이렇게 변호를 해주고 있습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 644.73,
      "end": 645.41,
      "text": "No,"
    },
    {
      "start": 645.71,
      "end": 646.09,
      "text": "아니야."
    },
    {
      "start": 646.51,
      "end": 647.43,
      "text": "Not this girl."
    },
    {
      "start": 647.95,
      "end": 649.57,
      "text": "이 여자는 그렇지 않다고."
    },
    {
      "start": 650.01,
      "end": 650.69,
      "text": "라고 하고 있어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 650.87,
      "end": 651.11,
      "text": "Ah,"
    },
    {
      "start": 651.17,
      "end": 652.43,
      "text": "the pizza delivery girl."
    },
    {
      "start": 652.59,
      "end": 653.13,
      "text": "I see."
    },
    {
      "start": 653.39,
      "end": 654.15,
      "text": "Not this girl."
    },
    {
      "start": 654.29,
      "end": 655.29,
      "text": "She's different."
    },
    {
      "start": 656.55,
      "end": 658.05,
      "text": "She was taking care of me"
    },
    {
      "start": 658.05,
      "end": 659.09,
      "text": "and everything."
    },
    {
      "start": 659.45,
      "end": 659.75,
      "text": "와,"
    },
    {
      "start": 660.21,
      "end": 660.49,
      "text": "그래요."
    },
    {
      "start": 660.87,
      "end": 663.05,
      "text": "She was taking care of me."
    },
    {
      "start": 663.41,
      "end": 665.21,
      "text": "그녀는 나를 보살펴줬고"
    },
    {
      "start": 665.21,
      "end": 666.17,
      "text": "and everything."
    },
    {
      "start": 666.47,
      "end": 667.61,
      "text": "모든 걸 다 해줬어."
    },
    {
      "start": 667.71,
      "end": 669.61,
      "text": "친절하게 나를 다 돌봐줬다고."
    },
    {
      "start": 669.93,
      "end": 670.53,
      "text": "She did."
    },
    {
      "start": 670.63,
      "end": 670.89,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 670.99,
      "end": 673.01,
      "text": "She took really good care of her."
    },
    {
      "start": 673.01,
      "end": 673.67,
      "text": "그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 673.67,
      "end": 675.35,
      "text": "Gave her everything she needed."
    },
    {
      "start": 675.41,
      "end": 675.57,
      "text": "Yeah,"
    },
    {
      "start": 675.67,
      "end": 676.55,
      "text": "as much as possible."
    },
    {
      "start": 676.55,
      "end": 676.67,
      "text": "A warm home,"
    },
    {
      "start": 676.91,
      "end": 677.27,
      "text": "food,"
    },
    {
      "start": 677.65,
      "end": 678.65,
      "text": "a loving heart,"
    },
    {
      "start": 679.07,
      "end": 679.99,
      "text": "shared her whole,"
    },
    {
      "start": 680.23,
      "end": 681.11,
      "text": "everything with her."
    },
    {
      "start": 681.17,
      "end": 681.45,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 682.55,
      "end": 684.35,
      "text": "She would even sing to me."
    },
    {
      "start": 684.89,
      "end": 687.38,
      "text": "She would even sing to me."
    },
    {
      "start": 687.38,
      "end": 689.14,
      "text": "저 이 장면 기억이 납니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 689.76,
      "end": 691.42,
      "text": "그녀가 이 트러블 앞에서"
    },
    {
      "start": 691.42,
      "end": 694.32,
      "text": "오디션에 갖고 가서 부를 노래를"
    },
    {
      "start": 694.32,
      "end": 695.72,
      "text": "미리 연습도 하고 그랬잖아요."
    },
    {
      "start": 695.94,
      "end": 696.78,
      "text": "그 작곡한 거."
    },
    {
      "start": 696.86,
      "end": 698.5,
      "text": "She's trying to make her own song"
    },
    {
      "start": 698.5,
      "end": 698.76,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 698.9,
      "end": 699.8,
      "text": "for that competition."
    },
    {
      "start": 699.98,
      "end": 700.2,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 700.3,
      "end": 702.44,
      "text": "She performed in front of Trouble."
    },
    {
      "start": 702.44,
      "end": 702.86,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 703.26,
      "end": 704.68,
      "text": "I think dogs like it."
    },
    {
      "start": 705.9,
      "end": 707.62,
      "text": "강아지들이 노래를 듣는 걸"
    },
    {
      "start": 707.62,
      "end": 709.08,
      "text": "되게 좋아한다고 저는 생각해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 709.2,
      "end": 710.94,
      "text": "Unless you're a huge 음치."
    },
    {
      "start": 712.06,
      "end": 713.44,
      "text": "Then they start barking."
    },
    {
      "start": 713.88,
      "end": 714.7,
      "text": "아, 진짜요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 714.82,
      "end": 715.12,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 715.38,
      "end": 716.44,
      "text": "If you're like tone deaf"
    },
    {
      "start": 716.44,
      "end": 717.82,
      "text": "and you can't sing a song,"
    },
    {
      "start": 718.02,
      "end": 718.7,
      "text": "dogs,"
    },
    {
      "start": 718.9,
      "end": 720.22,
      "text": "they have a very sensitive"
    },
    {
      "start": 720.22,
      "end": 721.46,
      "text": "sense of hearing."
    },
    {
      "start": 721.72,
      "end": 723.64,
      "text": "So their ears are very sensitive."
    },
    {
      "start": 723.82,
      "end": 725.26,
      "text": "So have you experienced that?"
    },
    {
      "start": 725.4,
      "end": 725.76,
      "text": "Sure."
    },
    {
      "start": 725.88,
      "end": 726.36,
      "text": "Oh, really?"
    },
    {
      "start": 726.36,
      "end": 727.42,
      "text": "I grew up with dogs."
    },
    {
      "start": 727.54,
      "end": 728.28,
      "text": "Did it bark?"
    },
    {
      "start": 728.78,
      "end": 730.24,
      "text": "If they hear sounds they don't like,"
    },
    {
      "start": 730.68,
      "end": 732.0,
      "text": "they whine"
    },
    {
      "start": 732.0,
      "end": 733.74,
      "text": "or they just run away."
    },
    {
      "start": 733.9,
      "end": 734.34,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 735.02,
      "end": 736.04,
      "text": "At least my dog."
    },
    {
      "start": 736.6,
      "end": 737.16,
      "text": "How wise."
    },
    {
      "start": 737.34,
      "end": 737.94,
      "text": "How wise."
    },
    {
      "start": 737.96,
      "end": 739.0,
      "text": "My dog was like that."
    },
    {
      "start": 739.06,
      "end": 739.3,
      "text": "Wow."
    },
    {
      "start": 739.48,
      "end": 741.04,
      "text": "똑똑한 강아지를 키우셨군요."
    },
    {
      "start": 741.06,
      "end": 741.88,
      "text": "네, 그럼요."
    },
    {
      "start": 742.26,
      "end": 744.86,
      "text": "강아지들은 대부분 노래 불러주면 되게 좋아하는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 744.86,
      "end": 746.76,
      "text": "그리스 씨가 이야기하신 것에"
    },
    {
      "start": 746.76,
      "end": 748.56,
      "text": "아주 빵빵 터지시는 분들 계실 겁니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 748.74,
      "end": 750.56,
      "text": "If you sing a song for a dog,"
    },
    {
      "start": 750.64,
      "end": 752.24,
      "text": "I'm sure the dog will love it."
    },
    {
      "start": 752.24,
      "end": 754.02,
      "text": "Oh, kind."
    },
    {
      "start": 754.02,
      "end": 758.58,
      "text": "네, 그래서 그녀는 심지어 나에게 노래를 불러줬다고"
    },
    {
      "start": 758.58,
      "end": 759.68,
      "text": "라고 변호해요."
    },
    {
      "start": 759.82,
      "end": 760.82,
      "text": "She liked me."
    },
    {
      "start": 760.88,
      "end": 762.8,
      "text": "그녀는 나를 좋아한다고."
    },
    {
      "start": 763.8,
      "end": 766.0,
      "text": "What are you doing in here anyway?"
    },
    {
      "start": 766.76,
      "end": 767.56,
      "text": "근데, 라우지,"
    },
    {
      "start": 767.84,
      "end": 769.94,
      "text": "what are you doing in here anyway?"
    },
    {
      "start": 770.28,
      "end": 771.56,
      "text": "또 여기에 왜 있는 거야?"
    },
    {
      "start": 771.88,
      "end": 773.1,
      "text": "라고 물어봅니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 773.36,
      "end": 774.12,
      "text": "That's a good question."
    },
    {
      "start": 774.14,
      "end": 774.6,
      "text": "그러게요."
    },
    {
      "start": 774.82,
      "end": 775.02,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 775.26,
      "end": 776.9,
      "text": "Why are we all in this pound?"
    },
    {
      "start": 777.12,
      "end": 778.5,
      "text": "Well, I know why I got here."
    },
    {
      "start": 778.56,
      "end": 779.76,
      "text": "But why are you here?"
    },
    {
      "start": 779.76,
      "end": 781.84,
      "text": "저도 되게 궁금했는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 781.84,
      "end": 784.26,
      "text": "여기서 트러블이 제대로 질문을 해줘서"
    },
    {
      "start": 784.26,
      "end": 785.06,
      "text": "아주 고마웠어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 785.22,
      "end": 785.76,
      "text": "That's a good question."
    },
    {
      "start": 785.86,
      "end": 787.3,
      "text": "I was wondering the same thing."
    },
    {
      "start": 787.4,
      "end": 787.54,
      "text": "Yeah."
    },
    {
      "start": 787.96,
      "end": 789.32,
      "text": "이 장면 한 번 더 들어보겠습니다."
    },
    {
      "start": 790.4,
      "end": 791.4,
      "text": "There's been a mistake."
    },
    {
      "start": 791.7,
      "end": 792.94,
      "text": "I don't belong here."
    },
    {
      "start": 793.18,
      "end": 794.26,
      "text": "I didn't do anything."
    },
    {
      "start": 794.48,
      "end": 796.18,
      "text": "I tried to tell you."
    },
    {
      "start": 796.42,
      "end": 796.92,
      "text": "라우지?"
    },
    {
      "start": 797.22,
      "end": 798.5,
      "text": "Humans can't be trusted."
    },
    {
      "start": 798.94,
      "end": 800.76,
      "text": "It's a story as old as time."
    },
    {
      "start": 800.96,
      "end": 801.86,
      "text": "When things go bad,"
    },
    {
      "start": 801.96,
      "end": 803.16,
      "text": "first thing humans do"
    },
    {
      "start": 803.16,
      "end": 804.76,
      "text": "is get rid of the dog."
    },
    {
      "start": 804.98,
      "end": 806.22,
      "text": "No, not this girl."
    },
    {
      "start": 806.22,
      "end": 808.14,
      "text": "She was taking care of me and everything."
    },
    {
      "start": 808.66,
      "end": 809.74,
      "text": "She would even sing to me."
    },
    {
      "start": 810.34,
      "end": 811.22,
      "text": "She liked me."
    },
    {
      "start": 811.22,
      "end": 813.59,
      "text": "What are you doing in here anyway?"
    },
    {
      "start": 814.92,
      "end": 816.96,
      "text": "네, 이 위기의 순간을"
    },
    {
      "start": 816.96,
      "end": 819.14,
      "text": "잘 헤쳐나갔으면 좋겠어요."
    },
    {
      "start": 819.4,
      "end": 819.54,
      "text": "그렇죠?"
    },
    {
      "start": 820.38,
      "end": 821.56,
      "text": "생각해보니까"
    },
    {
      "start": 821.56,
      "end": 824.56,
      "text": "제가 강아지한테 노래를 불러줬을 때"
    },
    {
      "start": 824.56,
      "end": 826.92,
      "text": "대부분의 경우는 강아지가 참 좋아했었는데"
    },
    {
      "start": 826.92,
      "end": 829.04,
      "text": "When I sang too much"
    },
    {
      "start": 829.04,
      "end": 830.98,
      "text": "너무 많이 노래를 불러주잖아요?"
    },
    {
      "start": 831.26,
      "end": 833.56,
      "text": "아무리 노래를 잘 불러준다 한들"
    },
    {
      "start": 833.56,
      "end": 834.36,
      "text": "강아지가"
    },
    {
      "start": 834.36,
      "end": 836.02,
      "text": "He tried to stop me."
    },
    {
      "start": 836.54,
      "end": 837.06,
      "text": "How?"
    },
    {
      "start": 837.06,
      "end": 838.8,
      "text": "어떻게 했냐면 주로"
    },
    {
      "start": 838.8,
      "end": 839.12,
      "text": "이제"
    },
    {
      "start": 839.12,
      "end": 840.04,
      "text": "licked me"
    },
    {
      "start": 840.04,
      "end": 840.48,
      "text": "Oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 840.48,
      "end": 841.94,
      "text": "And it went to the other room"
    },
    {
      "start": 841.94,
      "end": 842.52,
      "text": "Oh"
    },
    {
      "start": 842.52,
      "end": 843.44,
      "text": "Okay, that's enough"
    },
    {
      "start": 843.44,
      "end": 844.38,
      "text": "That's enough"
    },
    {
      "start": 844.38,
      "end": 845.46,
      "text": "적당히 좀 해"
    },
    {
      "start": 845.46,
      "end": 846.02,
      "text": "그만해"
    },
    {
      "start": 846.02,
      "end": 846.44,
      "text": "하고"
    },
    {
      "start": 846.44,
      "end": 847.06,
      "text": "받아주고"
    },
    {
      "start": 847.06,
      "end": 848.52,
      "text": "이제 다른 방으로 가버리고"
    },
    {
      "start": 848.52,
      "end": 850.12,
      "text": "So even if you have a good voice"
    },
    {
      "start": 850.12,
      "end": 850.56,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 850.56,
      "end": 852.22,
      "text": "아, 참 강아지들"
    },
    {
      "start": 852.22,
      "end": 853.52,
      "text": "참 도도할 때가 있단 말이죠"
    },
    {
      "start": 853.52,
      "end": 854.82,
      "text": "Dogs are very honest"
    },
    {
      "start": 854.82,
      "end": 855.22,
      "text": "Yeah"
    },
    {
      "start": 855.22,
      "end": 856.36,
      "text": "With their feelings"
    },
    {
      "start": 856.36,
      "end": 859.12,
      "text": "네, 오늘 스크린 잉글리쉬는 여기까지입니다"
    },
    {
      "start": 859.12,
      "end": 860.66,
      "text": "그리스 씨, 내일 또 만나요"
    },
    {
      "start": 860.66,
      "end": 861.56,
      "text": "I'll see you tomorrow"
    }
  ]
}